title: Oxygen spillover from RuO2 to MoO3 enhances the activity and durability of RuO2 for acidic oxygen evolution
content:
Energy Environ. Sci., 2024, Advance Article
DOI: 10.1039/D4EE02549K, Paper
Wangyan Gou, Shishi Zhang, Yichen Wang, Xiaohe Tan, Linqing Liao, Zening Qi, Min Xie, Yuanyuan Ma, Yaqiong Su, Yongquan Qu
Oxygen spillover strategy of *O intermediate from RuO2 to MoO3 within RuO2/MoO3 catalysts can significantly suppress over-oxidation and dissolution of RuO2, which contributes to both high activity and durability for oxygen evolution in 0.5 M H2SO4.
